####  KNOW ISSUES

## GtkColorChooserWidget is buggy
It fails sometimes when you choose a color from dialog (it seems a gtk3 bug because worked fine on gtk2).

## gtk_paned_set_position does not work on init
It works fine afterthat.

## Image does not scale to smaller
It works if it grows. *preserve_aspect_ratio* is hardcored to TRUE because this.


